title: Wario and Waluigi Are the Superior Duo, and This Fan-Art Proves It [22 Pics]
text:
Tweet Posted: Tue, 1/31/2017 - 2:47am by Tyler Davidson 
It’s been quite some time since the dark counterparts of the Mario Bros., Wario and the much less creatively named Waluigi, slimed their way into our hearts. Yet somehow, there are still those members of the unwashed masses who simply don’t appreciate their brilliance. Maybe it's because the true nature of their relationship is so hazy ? In any event, Wario and Waluigi are clearly better than those other mustachioed plumbers, and over at DeviantArt, more enlightened minds prevail. So here are 18 examples of dope fan art that showcase just why Wario and Waluigi are the UNDISPUTED better duo. 1.
